Call me back, okay?

563
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,180
Ms. Zhou,

564
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,940
just now, Ms. Shi's team called.

565
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,860
They're coming earlier than planned this afternoon.

566
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:49,330
They'll be here in about half an hour.

567
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:51,620
That's good, let's finalize the deal early.

568
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,900
Did you notify Mr. Dong and Mr. Qin?

569
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,660
Yes.

570
00:27:54,830 --> 00:27:56,050
Mr. Dong arrived early this morning

571
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:57,900
and is preparing with Ji Jie and the others.

572
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,770
Alright then.

573
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,490
Also, Ms. Zhou,

574
00:28:03,070 --> 00:28:03,980
there's another matter.

575
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:06,700
A bit tricky.

576
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:12,050
Ms. Qiao,

577
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,330
if the family won't sign,

578
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:14,940
can't Yan Tong sign the consent herself?

579
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,180
She's only seventeen.

580
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:16,810
Shuyang,

581
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,380
Shuyang, which operating room?

582
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:20,330
OR 9. Did she sign the consent?

583
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,380
She didn't.

584
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:27,180
Ms. Qiao,

585
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:29,530
we've been emphasizing

586
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,940
standardized surgical procedures lately.

587
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:31,940
This...

588
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,250
This is a matter of life and death.

589
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:34,420
We can't afford to follow all the protocols right now.

590
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:36,980
Ms. Zhou,

591
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:44,460
why can't you just talk outside?

592
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,900
Why all the secrecy?

593
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:48,900
Why are Yan Dan and Yan Tong here?

594
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:50,770
Yan Dan called me in the middle of the night asking for help.

595
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,940
I brought the patient in for emergency treatment.

596
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:52,730
What's the problem?

597
00:28:53,510 --> 00:28:55,220
If there's no issue, then why won't she sign?

598
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,860
Didn't you say you'd stay out of it

599
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:57,770
because of Li Qi?

600
00:28:57,790 --> 00:28:59,140
Why the sudden concern?

601
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,660
Because I trust you, that's why.

602
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:02,530
Qiao Yang,

603
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:04,050
things are different now.

604
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:06,050
Shi Jin will be here in two hours.

605
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,290
Just two hours.

606
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:09,250
They could decide the fate of Gemu.

607
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:10,140
Do you understand?

608
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:12,530
That girl needs surgery immediately.

609
00:29:12,550 --> 00:29:14,220
She's already delirious from the fever.

610
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:15,420
She won't last much longer.

611
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,220
I know.

612
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:17,290
The infection is serious.

613
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,900
We need to start antibiotics first.

614
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:21,140
Once her white cell count drops, we'll operate.

615
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:22,620
Qiao Yang, it's just two hours.

616
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:24,180
Have you seen her leg?

617
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:24,940
Two more hours,

618
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,140
she'll lose the leg.

619
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,330
I've seen it.

620
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:28,420
Two hours won't make a difference.

621
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,420
How can you say that?

622
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:30,730
It's not your leg!

623
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:31,050
Seriously,

624
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:32,810
why are you so difficult to talk to?

625
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:33,860
Ms. Zhou,

626
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,810
Ms. Shi and her team have arrived. What do we do?

627
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:40,770
Give me a moment.

628
00:29:47,110 --> 00:29:47,900
Zhou Jingwen!

629
00:29:48,550 --> 00:29:49,330
Zhou Jingwen!

630
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:50,980
What's your problem?

631
00:29:51,350 --> 00:29:52,140
Zhou Jingwen!

632
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,250
Open the door!

633
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:56,980
This is illegal detention!

634
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,220
I'll call the police on you!

635
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:00,620
Open the door!

636
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,380
Ms. Shi,

637
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:14,660
welcome!

638
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:17,980
White coats...

639
00:30:18,310 --> 00:30:19,090
Nice.

640
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:22,570
It's been a long time since I've seen you all in white coats.

641
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:25,140
It feels like we're back in the old days.

642
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,380
Really brings back memories.

643
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:32,180
Didn't Mr. Chu say Qiao Yang is also at Gemu?

644
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,810
Why haven't we seen her?

645
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:36,700
Mr. Chu had a last-minute meeting.

646
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:38,090
He asked Qiao Yang to accompany him.

647
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:39,860
Zhou Jingwen.

648
00:30:41,590 --> 00:30:42,570
Oh, right.

649
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:45,010
He said he'd be arriving a bit later.

650
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:45,380
Yeah.

651
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:49,330
Sorry, I have to take this call.

652
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:51,180
I'll let the "ladies" friend" keep you company.

653
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:51,980
Hello?

654
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,730
Me.

655
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,530
Friend of the ladies!

656
00:30:57,510 --> 00:30:58,460
This way.

657
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:01,810
It's okay.

658
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,490
I know you're in Shenzhen.

659
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:05,380
No need.

660
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,730
Really, Mr. Jiang,

661
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:07,570
I'm here. I've got this.

662
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,980
Tang's just being childish.

663
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:12,090
Acts on impulse.

664
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,050
Okay, I understand.

665
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:15,730
Don't worry.

666
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:17,380
No matter what, we'll get this done today.

667
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,660
Acquiring Gemu won't change.

668
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,140
Alright.

669
00:31:22,310 --> 00:31:22,980
Sure.

670
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:25,180
Mr. Wang, Mr. Jiang wants to talk to you.

671
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:27,900
Hello, Mr. Jiang.

672
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:30,290
Don't worry.

673
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,380
Where are you?

674
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:41,940
I'm already here, where are you?

675
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,050
You think I feel good

676
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:46,180
about how things turned out?

677
00:31:47,310 --> 00:31:49,900
All this time, I've been juggling things at the company.

678
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:50,730
And for what?

679
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:51,940
To find someone better

680
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:53,250
suited to take over.

681
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:55,140
You told me to meet

682
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,250
that Shi person.

683
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,220
I did.

684
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,980
But I don't think she's straightforward enough,

685
00:31:59,000 --> 00:31:59,940
or sincere enough.

686
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:01,420
Come on, this is a big deal.

687
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,940
She needs time.

688
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:04,700
I'm telling you,

689
00:32:04,790 --> 00:32:07,050
She and her team are at Gemu right now, doing an inspection.

690
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,660
Tang Jun,

691
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,810
you absolutely cannot sell Gemu to Li Qi.

692
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,770
You know exactly what kind of person she is.

693
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,330
I don't care what kind of relationship you have with her.

694
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:19,090
I won't allow you to harm Gemu.

695
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:21,090
Zhou Jingwen, if that's how you're going to talk to me,

696
00:32:21,110 --> 00:32:22,250
you're really pushing it now.

697
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,660
Yesterday,

698
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:25,570
right outside my dad's hospital room,

699
00:32:25,590 --> 00:32:27,460
they gave me an ultimatum.

700
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,180
If I don't show them some real action,

701
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:31,050
the company's no longer going to be our family's.

702
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,380
Alright then.

703
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,290
Ms. Shi's still doing the inspection, right?

704
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,380
Ask her.

705
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:36,810
If she's sincere about taking over,

706
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:37,900
tell her to come find me.

707
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:38,810
If not,

708
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,010
then it'll be Li Qi.

709
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:40,980
It doesn't matter who it is,

710
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:43,180
I need to wrap this up today.

711
00:32:43,590 --> 00:32:44,620
Wait, Tang Jun.

712
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,250
Hello?

713
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,420
Hello?

714
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,050
Hu,

715
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:58,290
once this is settled,

716
00:32:58,440 --> 00:33:00,290
I'll be able to clear all those debts.

717
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,290
As for the follow-up,

718
00:33:01,590 --> 00:33:03,380
I'll have to count on you.

719
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,090
No problem.

720
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:07,330
As long as you

721
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,980
handle this well,

722
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,770
we'll be on your side.

723
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:13,050
I've already warned you.

724
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,660
Don't lose the big for the small.

725
00:33:15,590 --> 00:33:17,660
The vast ocean is all yours.

726
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:19,570
Who cares about a little stream?

727
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,940
Aren't you answering the other call?

728
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:30,330
My head hurts. I'm gonna get in the car and rest a bit.

729
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,330
I'm in the storage room on the fourth floor.

730
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,330
Someone locked me in.

731
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,290
Hurry up and come save me!

732
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,220
Open the door.

733
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,340
What do you mean by this?

734
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,820
Ms. Qiao, sorry,

735
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,530
Ms. Zhou has given a strict order.

736
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,530
No one can let you out

737
00:34:17,550 --> 00:34:18,900
before the tour ends.

738
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:20,090
Please bear with it for now.

739
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:23,090
Traitor!

740
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,490
Alright.

741
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:37,210
This has a very noticeable effect

742
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:38,610
on tightening and firming the skin.

743
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,210
Would you like to try it?

744
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:43,210
This is a benefit from Mr. Qin and Mr. Dong.

745
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,740
Then I'll be next.

746
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:45,940
Sure, next.

747
00:34:46,110 --> 00:34:47,170
I wanna try.

748
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,380
Together!

749
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,690
So eager!

750
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,780
But I have to tell everyone,

751
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:55,650
today we'll only do half, alright?

752
00:34:55,710 --> 00:34:57,050
Next time, we'll have to come back for the rest.

753
00:35:20,230 --> 00:35:22,010
One, two, three, go!

754
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:39,340
There's a traffic jam, wait a minute.

755
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:43,090
My dear young master, what are you waiting for?

756
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,420
When it's time to cut the meat,

757
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,740
there are no real opponents.

758
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,340
Anyone who can take over is a friend.

759
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,780
But what if the one controlling it

760
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,300
is my ex-girlfriend who betrayed me?

761
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:53,130
And the one I've never gotten over?

762
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,690
Hu, you've got life experience.

763
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:57,740
Help me out.

764
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,900
Tell me, am I just...

765
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:00,820
asking for it?

766
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:03,460
Back then, so many women,

767
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:05,340
they all adored me, chased me,

768
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,820
clung to me, smothered me.

769
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:08,090
But not her.

770
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,090
She was so independent.

771
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:11,780
She made me feel like...

772
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:14,780
like an older sister. No, that's not quite right.

773
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:16,690
Anyway, she knew when to be gentle with me,

774
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:17,740
and when to criticize me.

775
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,010
Everything about her just felt right.

776
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,650
Her?

777
00:36:34,630 --> 00:36:35,300
Ms. Li.

778
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:36,530
See, I just got in touch with him.

779
00:36:37,030 --> 00:36:39,090
He said the GPS led him into a dead end.

780
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:40,460
His brain,

781
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:41,460
ugh, he never remembers the way.

782
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:43,210
Let's wait a bit longer, maybe twenty minutes or so.

783
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:44,780
Alright then.

784
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:57,170
Pretty?

785
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,260
Pretty?

786
00:36:58,670 --> 00:37:00,570
She's the most beautiful woman in the world.

787
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,570
At least, in my heart.

788
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,820
We've been apart for so many days.

789
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:06,050
Just thinking of her

790
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:07,460
makes me feel restless.

791
00:37:07,670 --> 00:37:09,490
Back when she was at home, I didn't feel anything.

792
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,050
But now that she's gone,

793
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,010
it's like every corner of the house

794
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:13,420
still smells like her.

795
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,740
And somehow, that's become my favorite scent.

796
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,690
Even with all her flaws,

797
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:19,820
I just can't bring myself to hate her.

798
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:20,570
Hu,

799
00:37:20,590 --> 00:37:21,980
in a situation like this,

800
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,530
what should I do?

801
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:27,210
When it comes to personal matters,

802
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:33,490
you have to solve them yourself.

803
00:37:35,590 --> 00:37:36,900
Not gonna lie, Hu,

804
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,460
that eye mask of yours is kinda flashy.

805
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:39,690
It's alright, just average.

806
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,570
I'm gonna rest for a bit.

807
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:43,820
That was a lot to take in.

808
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:53,900
Not bad.

809
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:58,820
This is Lu Ziyou, Dr. Lu.

810
00:37:58,840 --> 00:37:59,530
Dr. Lu,

811
00:37:59,550 --> 00:38:01,380
Ms. Qiao's been calling you non-stop.

812
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:07,380
Card.

813
00:38:25,710 --> 00:38:27,260
Why are you only getting here now?

814
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,210
What's wrong?

815
00:38:29,590 --> 00:38:30,300
Don't mention it.

816
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,050
Come on,

817
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:32,300
you're coming with me to save someone.

818
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:33,900
Wait for me in the operating room.

819
00:38:44,110 --> 00:38:44,900
Where's your sister?

820
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:46,340
She went to the restroom.

821
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:47,780
Ms. Qiao,

822
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:50,650
while my sister's not here, please treat me.

823
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,300
I can't live without my legs.

824
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,860
Please.

825
00:38:55,710 --> 00:38:56,490
Don't worry.

826
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:16,530
Hello, how can I help you?

827
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:18,690
Hello.

828
00:39:21,230 --> 00:39:21,900
Tong!

829
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,530
Sorry,

830
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:23,610
you're not allowed in here.

831
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:24,940
Is my sister inside?

832
00:39:25,110 --> 00:39:26,650
I already said we're not doing the surgery.

833
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:27,780
We didn't sign anything.

834
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:28,740
Touch me again and see what happens.

835
00:39:47,150 --> 00:39:47,820
Ms. Qiao,

836
00:39:48,230 --> 00:39:49,530
there's someone making a scene at the entrance.

837
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:54,740
Ms. Shi,

838
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:56,300
feel free to come anytime.

839
00:39:56,630 --> 00:39:57,610
Just ask for me directly.

840
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:58,460
Alright.

841
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:00,570
Also,

842
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:02,780
everyone can add Ji Jie on WeChat.

843
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,260
You'll get a discount if you go through her next time.

844
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:04,780
Great.

845
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:05,570
- Get your supervisor over here. - This way.

846
00:40:05,590 --> 00:40:06,260
Let me in.

847
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,420
We're in the middle of an emergency procedure.

848
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:08,940
Is this how Gemu handles patients, pushing them around?

849
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:09,300
No, it's not.

850
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,050
Get your supervisor over here.

851
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:11,420
I said I didn't sign anything.

852
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,900
- You can't operate. - What's going on?

853
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:13,820
Tell me,

854
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:15,090
why did you perform surgery on my sister

855
00:40:15,110 --> 00:40:16,050
without my consent?

856
00:40:16,110 --> 00:40:17,090
I didn't sign anything.

857
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:18,530
It's okay, I'll handle this.

858
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:19,690
- Calm down. - Wait a second.

859
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:20,820
What's going on?

860
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,980
Can I ask,

861
00:40:23,230 --> 00:40:25,420
why was the surgery performed without consent

862
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:26,260
from the patient's family?

863
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,050
Ask her.

864
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,740
What kind of surgery was it?

865
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,740
Who was the lead surgeon?

866
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,460
It was me.

867
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:34,340
It's her.

868
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,340
I didn't sign anything and she still insisted on operating on my sister.

869
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:38,050
Alright, wait a second.

870
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:40,050
Weren't you in a meeting?

871
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:43,610
I got called back for an emergency surgery.

872
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,210
Her sister

873
00:40:45,230 --> 00:40:46,860
has over a hundred infected lesions.

874
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:49,210
Because the best window for treatment was missed earlier,

875
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,650
her condition is now critical.

876
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,340
If we don't operate immediately,

877
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,420
her life will be in danger.

878
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:57,650
Why didn't you want the surgery?

879
00:40:59,000 --> 00:40:59,980
I don't trust her.

880
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:13,340
If that's your final decision,

881
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:17,010
I'm afraid I'll have to disappoint my mentor.

882
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:19,530
Do what you want then.

883
00:41:22,110 --> 00:41:23,300
I know what you're thinking.

884
00:41:23,590 --> 00:41:25,090
You think a few more hours won't make a difference.

885
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:26,530
But the patient really can't wait.

886
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,610
We shouldn't gamble with a patient's life,

887
00:41:29,630 --> 00:41:30,380
right?

888
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,860
If this hospital ends up shutting down,

889
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,690
at least we'll have a clear conscience for the rest of our lives.

890
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,820
But if we lose the patient,

891
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:38,780
I guarantee neither of us will be able to live with it.

892
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,650
If I don't go in, your sister will die.

893
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,900
Are you sure that's what you want?

894
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,340
Ms. Shi,

895
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,170
situations like this

896
00:42:08,190 --> 00:42:09,490
have never happened at our hospital before.

897
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:11,460
And I can promise you,

898
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:13,780
they absolutely will never happen again in the future.

899
00:42:15,670 --> 00:42:16,380
Don't worry.

900
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,860
What's the situation outside?

901
00:42:23,550 --> 00:42:24,490
A special situation.

902
00:42:27,710 --> 00:42:28,980
Let me tell you something.

903
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:31,170
By participating in this surgery,

904
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,490
we could all lose our jobs.

905
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,130
In the worst case scenario,

906
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:35,860
this hospital might go under because of it.

907
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:37,820
So think it through carefully.

908
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:39,130
It's your choice.

909
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,340
Well, we're already here.

910
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:42,780
Let's just do it.

911
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,380
Bringing down the whole hospital?

912
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,900
What an honor.

913
00:42:46,670 --> 00:42:47,490
Then let's do it.

914
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:53,980
I'll take care of the right leg.

915
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,380
You handle debridement on the left.
